### What mbuzz Offers

**All-channel attribution, not just ads.** Cometly tracks Meta, Google, and TikTok ads. mbuzz tracks every channel—organic search, email, referral, social, paid, direct. When 40% of your revenue comes from non-paid channels, Cometly has a massive blind spot.

