### Who mbuzz is NOT For

Let's be honest—mbuzz isn't right for everyone:

- **Teams who only run paid ads** — If ads are 90%+ of your business and CAPI enrichment is priority #1, Cometly is purpose-built for that
- **Non-technical teams wanting AI recommendations** — Cometly's "scale this, cut that" AI is easier than interpreting 8 models
- **Teams who want ad platform optimization, not attribution** — Different tools for different questions

### Best For

- Teams needing all-channel attribution (not just ads)
- Companies wanting transparent, inspectable models
- Server-side tracking for complete data capture
- Custom attribution logic for your business

